==Bio==
 
* Lecturer at the Insitute for Contemporary Art Research at the Zurich University of Arts with a focus on media economics
* co-founder of Openflows (an international open source research and development network.
Publications include
* ‘Open Cultures and the Nature of Networks’
* ‘Open Source Projects as Voluntary Hierarchies’
* ‘Kultur der Digitalität’ (2016) translated 2018 as ‘the digital condition’

